<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Trump&#8217;s New Proposal Cheats 8 Million Working People of Overtime Pay</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">
