<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/gop-marks-international-labor-day-by-pushing-death-of-mandatory-overtime-pay/">GOP Marks International Labor Day by Pushing Death of Mandatory Overtime Pay</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">A new proposal would allow employers to offer 1.5 hours of paid time off, for every hour worked over the 40-hour overtime threshold.</div>
</div>
</div>
